A film crew goes on an exploratory expedition to the Congo - where, hidden deep in the forest, they end up discovering some species of dinosaurs who should be extinct for 65 million years. But time has matured these predators, which once dominated the Earth, and quickly human explorers are put in the role of prey, running for their lives. When the tapes of this journey are found, the truth finally comes to light for those who thought they were extinct. Explosive mixture of "Jurassic Park" and "The Blair Witch Project"!
